{"ja499:0.1":"Jataka ","ja499:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja499:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja499:0.4":"3. Sivijataka ","ja499:1.1":"“Dure apassam therova, ","ja499:1.2":"cakkhum yacitumagato; ","ja499:1.3":"Ekanetta bhavissama, ","ja499:1.4":"cakkhum me dehi yacito”. ","ja499:2.1":"“Kenanusittho idha magatosi, ","ja499:2.2":"Vanibbaka cakkhupathani yacitum; ","ja499:2.3":"Suduccajam yacasi uttamangam, ","ja499:2.4":"Yamahu nettam purisena duccajam”. ","ja499:3.1":"“Yamahu devesu sujampatiti, ","ja499:3.2":"Maghavati nam ahu manussaloke; ","ja499:3.3":"Tenanusittho idha magatosmi, ","ja499:3.4":"Vanibbako cakkhupathani yacitum. ","ja499:4.1":"Vanibbato mayha vanim anuttaram, ","ja499:4.2":"Dadahi te cakkhupathani yacito; ","ja499:4.3":"Dadahi me cakkhupatham anuttaram, ","ja499:4.4":"Yamahu nettam purisena duccajam”. ","ja499:5.1":"“Yena atthena agacchi, ","ja499:5.2":"yamatthamabhipatthayam; ","ja499:5.3":"Te te ijjhantu sankappa, ","ja499:5.4":"labha cakkhuni brahmana. ","ja499:6.1":"Ekam te yacamanassa, ","ja499:6.2":"Ubhayani dadamaham; ","ja499:6.3":"Sa cakkhuma gaccha janassa pekkhato, ","ja499:6.4":"Yadicchase tvam tadate samijjhatu”. ","ja499:7.1":"“Ma no deva ada cakkhum, ","ja499:7.2":"ma no sabbe parakari; ","ja499:7.3":"Dhanam dehi maharaja, ","ja499:7.4":"mutta veluriya bahu. ","ja499:8.1":"Yutte deva rathe dehi, ","ja499:8.2":"ajaniye calankate; ","ja499:8.3":"Nage dehi maharaja, ","ja499:8.4":"hemakappanavasase. ","ja499:9.1":"Yatha tam sivayo sabbe, ","ja499:9.2":"sayogga saratha sada; ","ja499:9.3":"Samanta parikireyyum, ","ja499:9.4":"evam dehi rathesabha”. ","ja499:10.1":"“Yo ve dassanti vatvana, ","ja499:10.2":"adane kurute mano; ","ja499:10.3":"Bhumyam so patitam pasam, ","ja499:10.4":"givayam patimuncati. ","ja499:11.1":"Yo ve dassanti vatvana, ","ja499:11.2":"adane kurute mano; ","ja499:11.3":"Papa papataro hoti, ","ja499:11.4":"sampatto yamasadhanam. ","ja499:12.1":"Yanhi yace tanhi dade, ","ja499:12.2":"yam na yace na tam dade; ","ja499:12.3":"Svaham tameva dassami, ","ja499:12.4":"yam mam yacati brahmano”. ","ja499:13.1":"“Ayum nu vannam nu sukham balam nu, ","ja499:13.2":"Kim patthayano nu janinda desi; ","ja499:13.3":"Kathanhi raja sivinam anuttaro, ","ja499:13.4":"Cakkhuni dajja paralokahetu”. ","ja499:14.1":"“Na vahametam yasasa dadami, ","ja499:14.2":"Na puttamicche na dhanam na rattham; ","ja499:14.3":"Satanca dhammo carito purano, ","ja499:14.4":"Icceva dane ramate mano mama”. ","ja499:14.5":"(…) ","ja499:15.1":"“Sakha ca mitto ca mamasi sivika, ","ja499:15.2":"Susikkhito sadhu karohi me vaco; ","ja499:15.3":"Uddharitva cakkhuni mamam jigisato, ","ja499:15.4":"Hatthesu thapehi vanibbakassa”. ","ja499:16.1":"Codito sivirajena, ","ja499:16.2":"siviko vacanankaro; ","ja499:16.3":"Ranno cakkhunuddharitva, ","ja499:16.4":"brahmanassupanamayi; ","ja499:16.5":"Sacakkhu brahmano asi, ","ja499:16.6":"andho raja upavisi. ","ja499:17.1":"Tato so katipahassa, ","ja499:17.2":"uparulhesu cakkhusu; ","ja499:17.3":"Sutam amantayi raja, ","ja499:17.4":"sivinam ratthavaddhano. ","ja499:18.1":"“Yojehi sarathi yanam, ","ja499:18.2":"yuttanca pativedaya; ","ja499:18.3":"Uyyanabhumim gacchama, ","ja499:18.4":"pokkharanno vanani ca”. ","ja499:19.1":"So ca pokkharanitire, ","ja499:19.2":"pallankena upavisi; ","ja499:19.3":"Tassa sakko paturahu, ","ja499:19.4":"devaraja sujampati. ","ja499:20.1":"“Sakkohamasmi devindo, ","ja499:20.2":"agatosmi tavantike; ","ja499:20.3":"Varam varassu rajisi, ","ja499:20.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja499:21.1":"“Pahutam me dhanam sakka, ","ja499:21.2":"balam koso canappako; ","ja499:21.3":"Andhassa me sato dani, ","ja499:21.4":"marananneva ruccati”. ","ja499:22.1":"“Yani saccani dvipadinda, ","ja499:22.2":"tani bhasassu khattiya; ","ja499:22.3":"Saccam te bhanamanassa, ","ja499:22.4":"puna cakkhu bhavissati”. ","ja499:23.1":"“Ye mam yacitumayanti, ","ja499:23.2":"nanagotta vanibbaka; ","ja499:23.3":"Yopi mam yacate tattha, ","ja499:23.4":"sopi me manaso piyo; ","ja499:23.5":"Etena saccavajjena, ","ja499:23.6":"cakkhu me upapajjatha. ","ja499:24.1":"Yam mam so yacitum aga, ","ja499:24.2":"dehi cakkhunti brahmano; ","ja499:24.3":"Tassa cakkhuni padasim, ","ja499:24.4":"brahmanassa vanibbato. ","ja499:25.1":"Bhiyyo mam avisi piti, ","ja499:25.2":"somanassancanappakam; ","ja499:25.3":"Etena saccavajjena, ","ja499:25.4":"dutiyam me upapajjatha”. ","ja499:26.1":"“Dhammena bhasita gatha, ","ja499:26.2":"sivinam ratthavaddhana; ","ja499:26.3":"Etani tava nettani, ","ja499:26.4":"dibbani patidissare. ","ja499:27.1":"Tirokuttam tiroselam, ","ja499:27.2":"samatiggayha pabbatam; ","ja499:27.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","ja499:27.4":"dassanam anubhontu te”. ","ja499:28.1":"“Ko nidha vittam na dadeyya yacito, ","ja499:28.2":"Api visittham supiyampi attano; ","ja499:28.3":"Tadingha sabbe sivayo samagata, ","ja499:28.4":"Dibbani nettani mamajja passatha. ","ja499:29.1":"Tirokuttam tiroselam, ","ja499:29.2":"samatiggayha pabbatam; ","ja499:29.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","ja499:29.4":"dassanam anubhonti me. ","ja499:30.1":"Na cagamatta paramatthi kinci, ","ja499:30.2":"Maccanam idha jivite; ","ja499:30.3":"Datvana manusam cakkhum, ","ja499:30.4":"Laddham me cakkhum amanusam. ","ja499:31.1":"Etampi disva sivayo, ","ja499:31.2":"Detha danani bhunjatha; ","ja499:31.3":"Datva ca bhutva ca yathanubhavam, ","ja499:31.4":"Anindita saggamupetha thanan”ti. ","ja499:32.1":"Sivijatakam tatiyam. "}